### =====================================================================
### CMMC Ontology — v0.4.4 Delta Patch
### Base: cmmc-ontology-v0.4.3.ttl (merged master, 2026-04-19)
### Delta source: project_canon_morning_review_queue_phase1.md
###                + [CANON SOURCE — Phase 0 Routines Plumbing — 2026-04-25]
### Generated: 2026-04-25
### Stage: Verb 4 — /ontogize (incremental, runtime-build Phase 1)
###
### Apply by concatenating this fragment after the v0.4.3 class/property/invariant
### sections of cmmc-ontology-v0.4.3.ttl. No existing declarations are removed.
### Three new top-level classes (cmmc:LoopArtifact, cmmc:Routine,
### cmmc:ControlObjective) plus one subclass (cmmc:MorningReviewItem),
### three new object properties, eight new datatype properties, two SKOS
### concept schemes, three new cmmc:Invariant instances, and one inline
### SHACL NodeShape enforcing the status FSM and the missing-data payload rule.
###
### Phase 1 emits this TTL delta only. It does NOT load anything into the
### runtime cmmc Neo4j db (that is Phase 2's /knowledge-graph step). It does
### NOT write a constrained-write MCP server (Phase 2). Do not advance to
